mmarquee.automation.uiautomation

Interface IUIAutomation4

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IUIAutomation, IUIAutomation2, IUIAutomation3, com.sun.jna.platform.win32.COM.IUnknown
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IUIAutomation5

    public interface IUIAutomation4
extends IUIAutomation3
    Wrapper for the IUIAutomation4 COM interface. Extends the IUIAutomation3 interface to expose additional methods for controlling UI Automation functionality. Windows 10, version 1607 [desktop apps only] Windows Server 2016 [desktop apps only]
